@startuml
title FreshFood CI/CD (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor Dev
participant "GitHub Repo" as Repo
participant "GitHub Actions\nfreshfood-ci-cd" as GHA
participant "backend-ci\n(Python 3.10 + pytest)" as BCI
participant "frontend-ci\n(Node 20 + vite build)" as FCI
participant "build-and-publish-images" as CD
database "GHCR" as GHCR

Dev -> Repo: Push / Open PR\n(main|master)
Repo -> GHA: Trigger workflow\n(path filter backend/frontend/workflow)

par CI - Backend
  GHA -> BCI: Checkout + pip install\npytest -q tests
  BCI --> GHA: pass/fail
else CI - Frontend
  GHA -> FCI: Checkout + npm ci\nnpm run build
  FCI --> GHA: pass/fail
end

alt Event = push AND CI green
  GHA -> CD: Start image job
  CD -> GHCR: Push freshfood-backend:<sha>
  CD -> GHCR: Push freshfood-frontend:<sha>
  CD --> GHA: done
else Event = pull_request
  GHA -> GHA: Skip CD image push
end

note right of CD
As-is: workflow dung o muc\nbuild + push image, chua co\nstep deploy staging/prod.
end note

@enduml
